hopobject.body: Do you know what extension he's on? desconto allegra d Obviously cats and dogs are different. Cats can generally be fine for an eight-hour period, but they need human contact and stimulation. Dogs can go eight hours without going out, but it's tough, and that's why there's been a boom in the dog-walking and pet-sitting industries. This is a major new part of our economy, and it employs tens of thousands of people who provide pet care services for people who work.
